    <h3 class="c11 c62" id="h.t9i3lt61dfz8"><span class="c28"></span></h3>
    <p class="c39 c68 c74"><span class="c24">Coffee Stain Group is a Scandinavian game developer and publisher with a portfolio of community-driven games primarily for PC and console and a proven track record of building intellectual properties including Goat Simulator, Satisfactory, Deep Rock Galactic, Valheim, Teardown and Welcome to Bloxburg. The Group consists of 250 employees in 13 game studios including Coffee Stain, Ghost Ship and Tuxedo Labs - all united by the aspiration of &quot;</span><span class="c70 c24">small teams</span><span class="c24">&nbsp;making </span><span class="c24 c70">big games</span><span class="c24">&nbsp;for </span><span class="c70 c24">huge audiences</span><span class="c24 c77">&quot; </span></p>
